text.tspan: I want my food on time and freshly prepared.
Wale is a 24-year-old millennial professional who works
as an account manager in an advertising company in
Lagos, Nigeria. he lived in lekki and often drives to work.
pressured to reach his daily sales quota, Wale is often in
the field meeting and presenting to different
clients. When he is back at the office,he often does
admin work and telemarketing to reach more clients.
with wale's tight schedule, he needs his food to be
delivered on time and freshly prepared. He wants a wide
variety of food to choose from and also to be updated
with the delivery time so he knows when to receive his
Wale often uses promos with his colleagues so he can
save money and buy more. He prefers payment by the
app's wallet, giftcards or crypto as he does not want to
leave his bank details on the app.
